If you are watching this show expecting mindless action and no exposition, politics, etc, then you are watching the wrong show. This is a series for adults -- maybe you should stick with Power Rangers and DBZ.

You kids DO know that this show follows the books do you not?  Books....you know stacks of papers with written words bound together.  Turn off the TV go get the books and you'll find out if there even are dragons in Game of Thrones.

This series follows the books almost exactly as written, not like the rewritten Ring trilogy and the books are some of the best in the "fantasy" genre despite the lack of overpowered magicians and horde of dragons and monsters. The big thing with these are actually the politics and plots so if you dont like them I advise you to follow hettbeans advice.
